name: Sweeping a bamboo floor
description:
0:00 - 0:17 Getting the broom from the closet
0:18 - 0:55 Sweeping, starting far away and getting closer to the microphone
0:56 - 1:26 Getting the dust pan and dumping the sweepings, putting everything away

The bamboo floor is interesting because you can hear the gaps between the slats as the broom passed over them.
